{"tid":1590073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10.1 唔係要組臨時立法會/政府咩?又無左件事?","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:29:55.000Z","uid":29514,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f46f7cb8760eeee40b81b9534189b9be301fec4a","tid":1590073,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"10.1和理非好, 勇武又好都唔係問題, 最重要既係10.1要做D更爆,更令全世界注目係香港既野,如果一直都係重覆之前既野就算係和理非定勇武其實都無咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨時立法會/政府唔等於大台,但大家宣佈左出黎就可以用呢樣野取代五大訴求, 成為運動既新目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將來既行動就可以向住呢個目標進發, 我建議10.1十八區各自搵個地方舉行誓師大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />向全世界人展示香港人既決心"},{"pid":"2ee578918fb86ac3043994e36219a314d74bd75d","tid":1590073,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"［行動post］10.1 維港悼念活動 燭光晚會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588919</a><br />\n<br />\n10月1日<br />\n晚上8點<br />\n維港兩岸<br />\n讓燭光燃點維港<br />\n悼念新屋嶺 &amp; 太子831 &amp; 運動中被逼害人士及死難者<br />\n<br />\n平反新屋嶺 平反831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /